Nazro ki khidkiyo par ye pardo ki parte chadhayge,
Darwaze khauf me band hi rahe, 
Bhram aisa  ye failayge.
Inhe khabar hain, jo apas me
Nain humare takrayge,
Kiraye ke inke jo makaan hain,
Neev se chat tak, hil jaege.
Unki eeto pe laga khoon 
Fir thar thar hokar chillayga,
Daba hua hain arso se,
 us bhed ko khol jaega,
Ki chala jaa raha hain sadiyo se ,
Jhoota wo farmaan hain.
Aur tum bhi bus insaano ho,
Aur hum bhi bus insaan hain.
